# Referral Bridge — Full Project Context

## Overview

**Referral Bridge** is a Next.js 16 clinical trial patient recruitment landing page platform. It generates patient leads for clinical trials, collecting user data through a multi-step form, submitting it to **LeadsPedia** (lead aggregation platform), which then relays qualified leads to **HealthMatch** (trial matching partner). Currently operates a single active trial for **Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD)**.

- **Framework:** Next.js 16.2.6 (App Router, React 19.2.4, TypeScript 5)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS 4 (PostCSS plugin), custom CSS variables, no tailwind.config.ts
- **Deployment:** PM2 on port 3002 (`pm2 restart referral-bridge`)
- **Dev server:** `next dev --port 3001`
- **Base path:** `/lander` (all routes served under `https://goodlabgroup.com/lander/`)
- **Asset prefix:** `/lander`
- **Company:** Good Lab (clinical trial matchmaking service)

