## Active Trial: CKD-001 (Chronic Kidney Disease)

Configured in `lib/trials/ckd-001.ts`:

- **Trial ID:** `ckd-001`
- **Study Code:** `NB-2614`
- **Slug:** `chronic-kidney-disease`
- **Condition:** CKD
- **Partner:** HealthMatch
- **LeadsPedia Trial Code:** `ckd14`
- **HealthMatch Trial ID:** `AZCKDD6800C00005`
- **HealthMatch Condition ID:** `400`
- **Age Range:** 18–65
- **Duration:** 8–24 weeks
- **ZIP Eligibility:** ~5,500 US ZIP codes across 21+ states (stored in `lib/data/eligible-zips-ckd14.ts`)

### Screening Questions (10 total)
1. Height (feet/inches input)
2. Weight (pounds input)
3. CKD diagnosis (select: Yes currently / Yes in past / No / Not sure) — DQ on "No"
4. Dialysis (select: No / Yes / Previously) — DQ on "Yes"
5. Kidney transplant (boolean) — DQ on "Yes"
6. Diabetes (select: No / Type 2 / Type 1) — DQ on "Type 1"
7. Insulin use (boolean)
8. Excluded conditions (multiselect: Hep B/C, sickle cell, liver disease, long QT, bleeding disorder, cancer) — DQ on any
9. Recent events (multiselect: stroke, heart attack, coronary revascularization, organ transplant) — DQ on any
10. Clinical trial participation (boolean) — DQ on "Yes"
11. African ancestry (boolean) — informational, not DQ

### Contact Fields Collected
- firstName, lastName, email, phone, zipCode (Part 1)
- dob, sex, address (Part 2a)
- ethnicity (multiselect), doctorDetails (optional) (Part 2b)

### Consent Requirements
- HealthMatch Terms of Service & Privacy Policy
- EMR (medical records) consent authorization
- Site-specific consent (fetched dynamically via HealthMatch GraphQL per ZIP)

