## Trial Lander Page Structure

The `[trial]/page.tsx` server component renders these sections in order:

1. **Nav** — Logo + "Check eligibility" CTA button
2. **Hero** — 3fr/2fr grid: text column (subtitle, title, description, benefits list, "Read about the study" link) + form column (TrialForm component in blue card)
3. **Stats** — 2-column centered bar (Age 18–65, Duration 8–24 wks)
4. **About the Study** — Study headline, multi-paragraph description, eligibility criteria table
5. **CTA** — Dark blue section with headline, "Check eligibility" button, enrollment counter
6. **Why Participate** — 4 reasons with icons (Stethoscope, MapPin, DollarSign, ShieldCheck)
7. **About Us** — Company description, founded/HQ/sites/enrolled stats
8. **FAQ** — 5 accordion items
9. **Footer** — Logo, HIPAA badges, links (Terms, Privacy, Contact), copyright, social icons

