## Adding a New Trial

To add a new trial:

1. Create a new config file in `lib/trials/` (e.g. `new-trial.ts`) following the `TrialConfig` type
2. Register it in `lib/trials/index.ts` by importing and adding to the `trials` map
3. Create an eligible ZIP codes file in `lib/data/` if needed
4. Update ZIP validation in `api/leadspedia/route.ts` to handle the new trial
5. Update relay constants in `api/healthmatch-relay/route.ts` if routing to HealthMatch

