## Known Issues & Notes

- `zod` is listed as a dependency but not actively used in any route handlers or lib files
- Analytics PIN (`9021`) is client-side only — anyone inspecting the JS bundle can bypass it
- The `company.meta` block in `ckd-001.ts` says "Founded 2018, Boston MA" but the rendered HTML in `page.tsx` hardcodes "Founded 2021, Sydney AU"
- LeadsPedia credentials have hardcoded fallbacks in source code (should be env-only)
- ZIP gate is enforced both client-side (`trial-form.tsx`) and server-side (`api/leadspedia/route.ts`) — correct pattern
- Analytics NDJSON files use append-only writes (`fs.appendFileSync`) for concurrent safety
- All analytics timestamps use Australia/Sydney timezone (AEST) regardless of server timezone
